1 WHEREAS the elementary fitness meet has served as the Olympic Games for
2 elementary school-aged children in thirty parishes across the state since 1997, and more than
3 two hundred thousand students have competed for the state fitness crown.
4 THEREFORE, BE IT RESOLVED that the House of Representatives of the
5 Legislature of Louisiana does hereby commend and congratulate the students, coaches, and
6 parents of the Lafayette Parish School System on their first place finish in the Louisiana
7 Governor's Games Thirty-First Annual Elementary State Championship Fitness Meet and
8 does hereby encourage all of the participants to continue their excellent work and always
9 strive for greatness in competition.
